---
title: Mexican Chickpea Taquitos with Charred Corn Salsa
description: Taquitos, the close relative of enchiladas are in town tonight and we're excited for their stay. By switching beef to beans, you can still get all of your favourite Mexican flavours in this delicious veggie meal! Dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the black beans in this recipe with chickpeas due to local
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
